{"arkId":"cl010111897","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111897","modified ":"2025-12-10","title":"Buste de Fran\u00e7ois-Marie Arouet, dit Voltaire","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Buste de Fran\u00e7ois-Marie Arouet, dit Voltaire"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : apr\u00e8s 1760","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 550 - Elise Dosne-Thiers, Vitrine 1, Etag\u00e8re 1","room":"Salle 550, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1760,"endYear":"","imprecision":"apr\u00e8s","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Rosset, Claude Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1749","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1818","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Rosset, Jean Claude Fran\u00e7ois Joseph","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"1706","place":"Saint-Claude","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1786","place":"Saint-Claude","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q15971335"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"TH 166","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"buste ; sculpture","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Apr\u00e8s son installation \u00e0 Ferney, Voltaire rencontra son presque voisin Joseph Rosset, qui se proposa de faire son portrait. L\u0027entrevue eut lieu \u00e0 l\u0027automne 1765 et Rosset commen\u00e7a \u00e0 partir de 1767 \u00e0 fabriquer et vendre ces petits bustes qui devinrent vite sa sp\u00e9cialit\u00e9.\r\nLes fils de Joseph Rosset ont continu\u00e9 \u00e0 reproduire les cr\u00e9ations de leur p\u00e8re, mais en infl\u00e9chissant leur style d\u0027une mani\u00e8re un peu caricaturale.\r\nCe buste se d\u00e9marque de la premi\u00e8re production : le menton est plus relev\u00e9, le port de t\u00eate plus altier, et la bonhomie premi\u00e8re abandonn\u00e9e au profit d\u0027un langage plus soutenu. Le caract\u00e8re p\u00e9tillant du regard est soulign\u00e9 par les yeux dilat\u00e9s aux pupilles profond\u00e9ment creus\u00e9s. La draperie s\u0027enroule sur les \u00e9paules, telle une robe d\u0027int\u00e9rieur laissant para\u00eetre la chemise ouverte.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; ROSSET FEC. (sign\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027arri\u00e8re)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"21,8","displayDimension":"21,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14,4","displayDimension":"14,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"9,7","displayDimension":"9,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,3","displayDimension":"6,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9b\u00e8ne (socle)","placeOfCreation":"France (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Adolphe Thiers; legs Elise Dosne Thiers, 1880, suivant les volont\u00e9s de son mari et sous r\u00e9serve d\u2019usufruit de sa s\u0153ur F\u00e9licie Dosne qui y renonce et ex\u0